            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Getting rid of treesitter on the package. I agree with you, seems odd, since it's an optional component.\n\nI don't really understand why the treesitter stuff is in there. We should not be fetching nvim-treesitter in the snap package. So let's remove that.\n\nThe default build includes various treesitter parsers for C/lua/etc. But that does not involve nvim-treesitter at all.",
